{"tid":948310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國小姐選拔變AV秀　竟直播更衣裸體露點","createTime":"2018-12-20T03:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T05:37:28.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70022d29732c42e2d36df2c24c96cad58fd9ccde","tid":948310,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:15:51.000Z","msg":"近日法國正舉行法國小姐的選拔賽，電視台《TF1》也轉播這場秀，但不知是有心還是無意，鏡頭竟然公然直播參賽者在後台更衣的裸體露點姿態，頓時間讓觀眾誤以為轉台到了蓬萊仙山。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，日前《TF1》轉播這場法國小姐選拔賽事，但就在一段節目中，鏡頭直播參賽者在更衣間換衣的模樣，前方有主持人泰勒(Sylvie Tellier)訪問參賽者的畫面，但鏡頭更公然播出參賽者們露奶露點的狀態。這段畫面播出後，讓參賽者和觀眾們都相當傻眼，泰勒也承認這段裸體畫面，對參賽者和觀眾們都非常失禮，她也承認：「這是一個非常大的失誤，也讓這個節目崩壞。」<br />\n<br />\n導播布魯卡(Franck Broqua)則表示，原本他們設計拍攝後台花絮，是為了更貼近參賽者的自然動態，並稱原本彩排的時候都沒有出包。<br />\n<br />\n而受害最深的參賽者，就是20歲的亞奎丹小姐(Miss Aquitaine)巴聶索(Carla Bonesso)，她是被拍到裸體最多的人。他希望自己在重返球壇前過上普通人的生活。巴聶索事後也大批主辦單位不專業，也相信這是個失誤，但至於要不要正式向主辦單位投訴，巴聶索則說：「我不知道。」<br />\n<br />\n目前電視台已經在網路片段上撤下這段裸體畫面。而這次法國小姐，最後由23歲大溪地小姐(Miss Tahiti)查維絲(Vaimalama Chaves)奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1DTYtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1DTYtd.png&h=a20c7858&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQ6uwOf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQ6uwOf.png&h=831a2528&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808e5e3f70a5c838f51a6db79fa33ed8c5fb6dae","tid":948310,"uid":83958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裸體 露點？？？</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f9365fbc05670be8d1ec528fb0b99b0a34b0c5f","tid":948310,"uid":218026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fc7e9633c367c59a6ddf58479ded50769d57112b","tid":948310,"uid":47422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"大溪地呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/h080996er6d_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fh080996er6d_496_280%2F0&h=a3dd7841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c35b8eb23c16eae6f764ddf45393d33dbba5404","tid":948310,"uid":144843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a14d2828a8b4ca385b863ccaff00c8fde7282e3","tid":948310,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a44c17fad8a64c6c87b7ee50de032d2b1a11eaa","tid":948310,"uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"講撚到口臭<br />\n又係無連登份"},{"pid":"9e43cff703c9622f71cc93bd816285b6587f341f","tid":948310,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa68u9.png?_w=750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaaa68u9.png%3F_w%3D750&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14phv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=aa77bc01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa68u9.png?_w=750</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph5c15b5d0e95f6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pornhub.com%2Fview_video.php%3Fviewkey%3Dph5c15b5d0e95f6&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14phv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=12855374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph5c15b5d0e95f6</a><br />\n<br />\n得果少少野睇"},{"pid":"baa118c9af91b71658646d51154c11761d1c3c83","tid":948310,"uid":45788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugsNiJH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugsNiJH.gif&h=6afc2a28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9048260bd04951190b3a786e8346a08b8b5c706c","tid":948310,"uid":135767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"